flowchart TD
    A[User Opens BidWise] --> B{Authenticated?}
    B -- No --> C[Register / Login]
    C --> D[JWT Issued + Role]
    B -- Yes --> D

    D --> E{Role}

    %% Buyer flow
    E -- Buyer --> F[Create Project]
    F --> G[Project Published]
    G --> H[View Incoming Bids]
    H --> I[Compare Bids]
    I --> J{Accept Bid?}
    J -- Yes --> K[Create Order / Contract]
    J -- No --> L[Reject Bid or Keep Open]

    %% Seller flow
    E -- Seller --> M[Browse Open Projects]
    M --> N[Submit Bid]
    N --> O[Bid Stored]
    O --> P[Notify Buyer]
    P --> H

    %% Shared post-acceptance flow
    K --> Q[Messaging]
    K --> R[Notifications]
    K --> S[Delivery / Completion]
    S --> T[Review / Rating]

    %% Admin flow
    E -- Admin --> U[Admin Dashboard]
    U --> V[User Moderation]
    U --> W[Dispute Resolution]
    W --> X[Resolution Applied]
    X --> R